comments: LeVert (CLE) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Embiid (PHI) dribbles the ball off Markkanen's (CLE) right foot, and Markkanen's contact with the ball is incidental.
Markkanen (CLE) dives for the ball and keeps it in-bounds.
Harris (PHI) applies a stayed hand on Garland's (CLE) left arm and restricts his upward shooting motion during the driving shot attempt.
Maxey (PHI) moves laterally with Garland (CLE) during the drive, and marginal body contact occurs.
Harden (PHI) applies a slight forearm to Mobley's (CLE) right side, and marginal contact occurs.
Harris (PHI) moves alongside LeVert (CLE) in a legal guarding position, and LeVert leans in to initiate contact during the driving shot attempt.
Markkanen (CLE) applies a stayed forearm over Embiid's (PHI) right arm before correcting as Embiid begins his upward shooting motion, and marginal contact occurs on the driving shot attempt.

LeVert (CLE) makes legal contact to the ball and Embiid's (PHI) left hand that is a part of the ball prior to any incidental contact with his left arm during the driving shot attempt. The two also make incidental foot-to-foot contact on the play.
Mobley (CLE) extends his lower body into the path of Maxey (PHI) during the screen, and marginal contact occurs.
Maxey (PHI) extends his right forearm into Garland's (CLE) side and affects his SQBR. This contact occurs prior to Garland beginning his upward shooting motion.
Harden (PHI) does not lift his foot from the floor as he turns on his foot, and he maintains a legal pivot foot.
Mobley (CLE) reaches over Harden's (PHI) right arm and makes contact to his face and affects his SQBR. Prior to this contact, Mobley makes slight contact to the ball without tying it up.
Garland (CLE) stops in the path of Thybulle (PHI) during the in-bounds play, and the two make incidental foot-to-foot contact that causes Garland to fall.
Embiid (PHI) makes contact to the body of Mobley (CLE) that affects his SQBR as he begins the drive.
Okoro (CLE) commits a take foul on Harden (PHI).
Harris (PHI) is in a legal guarding position moving alongside of LeVert (CLE) and he contests the driving shot attempt without initiating any illegal contact.
Okoro (CLE) makes contact to Maxey's (PHI) left arm as he attempts to secure the rebound.
